'''
"""
FoodDelivery Application - Flask Backend

This application serves a food delivery platform with multiple pages including Dashboard, Restaurants, Menu, Item details,
Cart, Checkout, Orders, Tracking, and Reviews. Data is loaded from local text files and rendered dynamically.

The Flask routes correspond exactly to frontend URLs to ensure proper navigation without hardcoded URLs.

